name: "Block HTTPDNS"
description: "阻止常见 HTTPDNS / 私有 DoH / App 内置解析端点，强制更多请求回到 Egern DNS 与规则体系。偏激进，建议放在模块靠前位置。"
author: "Luke-Lab666"
homepage: "https://github.com/Luke-Lab666/ProxyKit"
icon: "shield.fill"

rules:
